window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Fate is the darkest curse of all. <br> <br> <b>Nadine</b> <br> <br> We’ve reclaimed Octavia Falls and are restoring what was turned to ruin, but the priestesses remain a threat. The Miriamic Coven is looking to us to protect them from those who seek to destroy everything, and our enemies will stop at nothing to disrupt our power. <br> <br> The Curse Breaker Wand is our last hope. We must venture to places beyond our understanding if we hope to bring an end to this conflict for good. The coven is depending on me, and if I can’t bring our people together, I'll lose the family I've created and be left alone in the remnants of our destruction. <br> <br> <b>Lucas</b> <br> <br> Nadine and I are discovering what it means to be a family, but the coven is still in shambles. <br> <br> The fate of our people stands on the precipice. There are mysteries that remain unsolved and dots we have yet to connect that will determine our future. The choices of a single spellcaster could end us all. We must be willing to unite… otherwise, the coven and all its witches will fade from the magical world, and our goddess will be lost to us for all eternity.</p>"; 
